NK081(zhu)007:5: 'jug pa'i las rim rnams bzhugs so //
NK081(zhu)007:6: rgyan dgram mchod pa bshams pa dang //
NK081(zhu)007:7: rgyas pa'i sbyin bsreg shar du btang //
NK081(zhu)007:8: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan la //
NK081(zhu)007:9: ba yu lnga dang mar khu dang //
NK081(zhu)007:10: shing shun phye ma lngas byugs te //
NK081(zhu)007:11: dri lnga'i chu yis ngad bskyed la //
NK081(zhu)007:12: mtshams nas bsgom pa'i dgos ched bar //
NK081(zhu)007:13: zhi ba'i las byang gzhung du bsnyag /de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin bsgom //
NK081(zhu)007:14: stong pa chen po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK081(zhu)007:15: spyod yul yongs su dag par sbyangs //
NK081(zhu)007:16: kun tu snang nas lha bskyed bar //
NK081(zhu)007:17: rol mo lta bu'i ting 'dzin bsgom //
NK081(zhu)007:19: yan lag lha bskyed bum chu rnams //
NK081(zhu)007:20: dbus su bsdus te ye shes lngas //
NK081(zhu)007:21: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab pa rnams //
NK081(zhu)007:22: bum chus me long gzugs brnyan la //
NK081(zhu)007:23: dbang gi lag len bzhin du bya //
NK081(zhu)007:24: ye shes dkyil 'khor spyan drangs bstim //
NK081(zhu)007:25: thur ma snyan gzhar smad tsher dang //
NK081(zhu)007:26: ljags bzhar so shing so mang dang //
NK081(zhu)007:27: chan pas dbang po'i skyon bdun bsal //
NK081(zhu)007:28: dbu rgyan snyan cha cod pan dang //
NK081(zhu)007:29: mgul chu phreng ba dpung rgyan dang //
NK081(zhu)007:30: phyag gdub zhabs gdub do shal dang //
NK081(zhu)007:31: na bza' sham thabs sku reg dang //
NK081(zhu)007:32: sems can gdan dang rin chen lnga //
NK081(zhu)007:34: rgyab brten zla ba'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK081(zhu)007:35: bco brgyad rgyan gyis mdzes par bya //
NK081(zhu)007:36: sku mdog dbu gsum phyag drug dang //
NK081(zhu)007:37: zhabs bzhi gdan ljags mche ba dang //
NK081(zhu)007:38: ral pa smin ma phyag mtshan dang //
NK081(zhu)007:39: dgu yis che ba'i mnga' gsol lo //
NK081(zhu)007:40: yang na mnga' gsol rgyan gyis mdzes //
NK081(zhu)007:41: ye shes dkyil 'khor spyan drangs bstim //
NK081(zhu)007:42: phyag btsal dam bca' phyag rgya dang //
NK081(zhu)007:43: kun bzang phyag rgya zhabs bsil tshe //
NK081(zhu)007:44: chu gtsang sru chab 'dag chal dang //
NK081(zhu)007:45: 'bru spos sman dang rin chen chus //
NK081(zhu)007:46: khrus gsol ras kyi sku phyi'o //
NK081(zhu)007:47: me tog bdug spos mar me dri //
NK081(zhu)007:48: bdud rtsi gsang mnan gtor ma dang //
NK081(zhu)007:49: lhag pa ting 'dzin sbyor dang sgrol //
NK081(zhu)007:50: 'dod pa'i yon tan glu ye shes //
NK081(zhu)007:51: bro gar ye shes su ra to //
NK081(zhu)007:52: bcu drug gar gyi mchod pa'o //
NK081(zhu)007:53: lhab lhub rnga dang ba dan dang //
NK081(zhu)007:54: phul zhing bran pho bran mo dang //
NK081(zhu)007:55: bu dang bu mo chung ma dang //
NK081(zhu)007:56: rol mo ye shes mchod bshags dang //
NK081(zhu)007:57: smon lam 'dod don gsol ba gdab //
NK081(zhu)007:58: tshogs kyi mchod pa gzhung bzhin dbul //
NK081(zhu)007:59: cho ga de dag las mkhan dang //
NK081(zhu)007:60: bla mas gyer len bsnol mar bya //
NK081(zhu)007:61: de nas bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK081(zhu)007:62: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni //
NK081(zhu)007:63: bla mas rdo rje nyungs dkar thogs //
NK081(zhu)007:64: slob mas me tog thogs nas ni //
NK081(zhu)007:65: bden pa brgyad kyis yun ring du //
NK081(zhu)007:66: bzhugs par gsol ba gdab par bya //
NK081(zhu)007:67: 'bru brgyad sngags kyis brtan byas te //
NK081(zhu)007:68: nyungs dkar me tog dor byas nas //
NK081(zhu)007:69: yon bdag slob mas bskor bar bya //
NK081(zhu)007:70: phyag btsal mi 'bral mngon gyur par //
NK081(zhu)007:71: bla mas smon lam gdab par bya //
NK081(zhu)007:72: rab gnas las kyi rim pa ru bi ma la mi tras mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK081(zhu)007:73: bri 'am brtsigs pa'i thabs bcas la //
NK081(zhu)007:74: bsreg shing brtsegs la me dar dgag /mda' bzhi dang ni zhags pa bri //
NK081(zhu)007:75: cha gsum gzhung srong dzaba tshogs dag /rdzogs nas lhag pa rdzas kyi las //
NK081(zhu)007:76: byas te hom gyi las rim ni //
NK081(zhu)007:77: thabs gsang de lha'i gzhal yas bskyed //
NK081(zhu)007:78: de nang rdo rje'i brag steng du //
NK081(zhu)007:79: ra skyes sga gong nyi zla'i steng //
NK081(zhu)007:80: sa bon las ni dam tshig gi //
NK081(zhu)007:81: me lha mdog mtshan ldan pa bskyed //
NK081(zhu)007:82: dbang bskur byin rlabs mdog mtshan ldan //
NK081(zhu)007:83: ye shes me lha snyan dbab drangs //
NK081(zhu)007:84: bstims te brtan par bzhugs pa las //
NK081(zhu)007:85: thun mong mchog dang sbyin bsreg dbul //
NK081(zhu)007:86: bstod pa bzod gsol 'dod pa'i don //
NK081(zhu)007:87: gsol gdab las bcol me mchod do //
NK081(zhu)007:88: bsreg lha mchod lugs rnam gsum las //
NK081(zhu)007:89: phyag tshad dbang po ma yin te //
NK081(zhu)007:90: me lha'i lto bar gzhal yas khang //
NK081(zhu)007:91: lha dang bcas pa rdzogs tshul skyed //
NK081(zhu)007:92: yan lag lhar ldan ye shes pa //
NK081(zhu)007:93: dbab drangs bstims te brtan pa la //
NK081(zhu)007:94: phyi yul mchod dang sbyin bsreg ni //
NK081(zhu)007:95: tshig gis bstod la sngags kyi dbul //
NK081(zhu)007:96: dgos smon skabs la spyi smon 'jug /dug gsum mchod pa'ang de bzhin no //
NK081(zhu)007:97: lhag pa hom gyi las rim mo //
NK081(zhu)007:98: srin lag lu gu rgyud sbrel te //
NK081(zhu)007:99: gzhal yas khang dang lha bskyed nas //
NK081(zhu)007:100: bro yi tshig dang sngags brjod de //
NK081(zhu)007:101: gar stabs skyod nas sprul pa spro //
NK081(zhu)007:102: zhing g.yos 'go ba'i lha dang phral //
NK081(zhu)007:103: bkug bstims bzas par gsal ba la //
NK081(zhu)007:105: rjes su mthun pa'i smon lam gdab //
NK081(zhu)007:106: lu gu rgyud kyi las rim mo //
NK081(zhu)007:108: sngon du dmigs pa'i rten bcas te //
NK081(zhu)007:109: thod par bcug la 'brub khung bzhag /kha yi blta phyogs chas gos dang //
NK081(zhu)007:110: las kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed nas ni //
NK081(zhu)007:111: las la gzud cing bden pa bdar //
NK081(zhu)007:112: sprul pa spros te pho nyas dgug /dbye bstim rgya bzhis bcing bsdams bya //
NK081(zhu)007:113: bzas par gsal ba gtor mas btug /phur pa'i rgyud dbyibs grangs byin rlabs //
NK081(zhu)007:114: gnas gdab khrus lung tshe lung dang //
NK081(zhu)007:115: gnyan po rang byung khro bos bsgral //
NK081(zhu)007:116: nyungs dkar gyis ni thugs dam bskul //
NK081(zhu)007:117: dam rgyas btug ci rgya khram brdeg /shes pa gnas spar ral gris gtub //
NK081(zhu)007:118: mtshon cha'i char dbab phye ma 'am //
NK081(zhu)007:119: ril bur las kyi dkyil 'khor la //
NK081(zhu)007:120: bsam pas dug gsum mchod par dbul //
NK081(zhu)007:121: stob cing zad par gsol bar bsam //
NK081(zhu)007:122: lhag pa rdzas kyi las rim mo //
NK081(zhu)007:124: kun mkhyen mi phyed brtse ba'i thugs //
NK081(zhu)007:125: rtog med mos ltar kun tu snang //
NK081(zhu)007:126: tha dad gcig bral rgyal ba la //
NK081(zhu)007:128: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor du //
NK081(zhu)007:129: 'jug pa'i las rim bri bar bya //
NK081(zhu)007:130: slob dpon khrus byas chas gos gon //
NK081(zhu)007:131: dkyil 'khor shar sgor gus pas 'dug /snyim par rin chen me tog ldan //
NK081(zhu)007:132: dkyil 'khor gsal byas bdun pa ltar //
NK081(zhu)007:133: zhugs pas dkyil 'khor lha rnams dang //
NK081(zhu)007:134: bdag nyid tha dad med pa'o //
NK081(zhu)007:135: slob ma gzhug par gsol btab pas //
NK081(zhu)007:136: lha rnams 'dzum byas gnang thob bsam //
NK081(zhu)007:137: slob ma khrus byas gdong g.yogs ldan //
NK081(zhu)007:138: tshig gis gsol btab ru yis dri //
NK081(zhu)007:139: bu yis lan gdab las mkhan gyis //
NK081(zhu)007:140: tshig gi dkyil 'khor drung du bkri //
NK081(zhu)007:141: sangs rgyas slob dpon sems can la //
NK081(zhu)007:142: byin rlabs snod du rung bya'i phyir //
NK081(zhu)007:143: sngags kyi lus dbul sbyin par bya //
NK081(zhu)007:144: tshe sba sprul spro bar chad bskrad //
NK081(zhu)007:145: sgrib pa bral nas sems nyid la //
NK081(zhu)007:146: cho ga gsum gyis lhar bskyed de //
NK081(zhu)007:147: go bgo lus srung slob ma yis //
NK081(zhu)007:148: gsol btab ru yis bdud rtsi blang //
NK081(zhu)007:149: tshig gis zhus te sngags kyi sbyin //
NK081(zhu)007:151: mchog gsum dam tshig thob par bsam //
NK081(zhu)007:152: snying gar rdor bzhag tshig ru dbog /tsan+dana chu dang bdud rtsi la //
NK081(zhu)007:153: khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin dang //
NK081(zhu)007:154: rdo rje sems dpas rab gnas bya //
NK081(zhu)007:155: tshig dang sngags sbyin snying gar bzhag /
NK081(zhu)007:156: 'di phyi'i legs nyes byed par bsam //
NK081(zhu)007:157: snang stong dbyer med don rtogs nas //
NK081(zhu)007:158: spyod pas 'khor ba'i dngos po la //
NK081(zhu)007:159: spyad kyang nyes med tshogs 'gyur bsgrags //
NK081(zhu)007:160: tshig dang sngags kyis me tog dor //
NK081(zhu)007:161: gang la phog pa'i yi dam dbog /sngags kyis dam dran gzugs skur bzhengs //
NK081(zhu)007:162: spyan drangs mnyes legs phrin las dag /gsol gdab bstim pas lhar gyur te //
NK081(zhu)007:163: mtshan gdags nan tan bsgom bzlas bya //
NK081(zhu)007:164: tshig dang sngags kyis mig phye ste //
NK081(zhu)007:165: ma rig mun bsal rang gnas mthong //
NK081(zhu)007:166: lha rtog ngo sprad dkyil 'khor bstan //
NK081(zhu)007:167: gros bya yun gyi khas blangs bya //
NK081(zhu)007:168: zag bcas tshogs sbyor zhol khang gis //
NK081(zhu)007:169: nyon mongs gdung ba'i dmag mi bzlog /mthong sgom skas la 'dzegs nas ni //
NK081(zhu)007:170: kun mkhyen mkhar gyi steng du phyin //
NK081(zhu)007:171: 'jug pa las rim bi ma las mdzad pa i thi //
